  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      197.54,
      290.71,
      221.27
    ],
    "text": "1. (1) This Act may be cited as the Social Security Contribution Levy (Amendment) Act, No. 24 of 2025.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      233.8,
      290.7,
      281.27
    ],
    "text": "(2) The provisions of this Act, other than the provisions of subsections (1) and (2) of section 2, shall come into operation on the date on which the Bill becomes an Act of Parliament.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      293.8,
      290.7,
      329.27
    ],
    "text": "(3) The provisions of subsections (1) and (2) of section 2 shall be deemed to have come into operation on February 18, 2025 and July 1, 2025 respectively.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      341.54,
      290.71,
      365.27
    ],
